{
  "stem": "4686.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said that I was bossing her too much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She still tells me that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not a garden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's just a backyard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our-- we had our own house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had the factory in the back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And originally it was a dairy product factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the-- the horse driven carts came into the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had a big backyard where they were able to turn around and get loaded and went off to deliver the milk products.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father owned the business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our way, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because-- because that was the business was there and we lived there and it was a business originally where you have to start very early morning when the milk start to come in and then get it produced, pasteurized, and made the milk into-- into cheese and butter or whatever.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was very, very early [LAUGHS] time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I only know about it from the stories.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Only later when that factory, the license was taken away, then my father started to repair and make machinery and milk cans for the industry.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'36, '37.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know exactly, something has to do with Jewish laws and problems with the suppliers who were not very happy to supply Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- I haven't got a clear answer on that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was too early in my time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was able.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was a very able man and a very hard working man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had his connection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was very well-liked in the trade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's why he was able to start working with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was a gentleman, a Hungarian gentleman in appearance, in-- in way of behaving.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had a high school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had beautiful writing.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
